BT 1 0 0 1 0 13.9805 Tm 7.875 TL /F1 5.25 Tf 0 0 0 rg (Even though I use unix like systems on a daily basis, I never really touched on the topic of SELinux even though it was released in year 2000 by NSA to open source community. While talking to one of my) Tj T* (fellow engineers about some customer projects, he mentioned SELinux several times. Not knowing how stuff actually works, sucks... So time to get my hands on at least the basics of SELinux.) Tj T* ET
